
'''Guide: The Health Canada Policy Toolkit for Public Involvement in Decision Making.'''

URL = http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/ahc-asc/pubs/_public-consult/2000decision/index-eng.php

=Description=

"Back in 2000 Health Canada published an excellent resource called The Health Canada Policy Toolkit for Public Involvement in Decision Making.
It is a complete toolkit with guidelines, about 50 techniques described in concise details and with useful suggestions, and also case studies and references. I highly recommend it as a definitive reference on the various options for effective public engagment within the Canadian context."
(http://www.cooptools.ca/node/79)


